      "rationale": "Founded November 2021, starting as a Facebook page answering juniors' admission questions and growing into a coaching operation with its own LMS, mobile app, publishing arm and a 60+ person team; the founder states he still answers the questions. Mission framed as 'Your aim to top private universities is our mission.' The name was chosen deliberately: 'Every builder burns a v1 sooner or later. The name is about what you do next.' - i.e. the brand encodes resilience and rebuilding rather than a first-try success.",
